author: djames
msg: Convert automatic memory management code into pure Python,
so as to ensure thread safety.
Register atexit function to destroy application pool before
(make_ob_pool): Return a brand new default pool to Python.
(apr_pool_t._mark_valid): Register weakref to parent, so that
we will be notified when the parent is destroyed.
